{"slides": [{"slide": [{"text": "Use Coggle to create your Words and Pictures book.", "audio": "s0_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-91471916-4118-4331-bcf3-5be87f99f1e2.png"}], "audio": "s0_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "Specify the voice or language to the left of your main node.", "audio": "s1_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-016cbf85-5ce4-436e-8fc2-b4cb29116ed9.png"}], "audio": "s1_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "Add images to the right in your Coggle with drag and drop.", "audio": "s2_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-d8a940db-8507-4ec9-b629-88ffd86df608.png"}], "audio": "s2_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "Images uploaded to Coggle are stored with Amazon.", "audio": "s3_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-774e1ced-da24-420f-ade9-2961d9a07c29.png"}], "audio": "s3_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "You can also enter the web address of some other image to include.", "audio": "s4_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-83207996-77e0-4c1e-a613-c0ce0031ca2c.png"}], "audio": "s4_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "Use square brackets to keep text together in a block.", "audio": "s5_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-e01e042d-53b7-4947-8f56-fd982bfc11a5.png"}], "audio": "s5_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "When your Coggle is complete, copy the web address.", "audio": "s6_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-185cd5f1-8260-4e6c-8529-5aa5d8974753.png"}], "audio": "s6_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "Run python with the Coggle address as a parameter. Copy the generated API address.", "audio": "s7_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-33bce452-4f70-4067-912a-dbffb9e050d6.png"}], "audio": "s7_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "Paste in your browser, then right click to save the results.", "audio": "s8_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-c2197a17-7135-4edd-bb6d-124932ce547c.png"}], "audio": "s8_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "Save them in the same folder as your Python code.", "audio": "s9_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-c178c289-2b9f-4302-81bc-5a56be4c224b.png"}], "audio": "s9_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "Run the code again with this file as a parameter.", "audio": "s10_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-9c4abff4-5821-47f2-883b-0f958bab1426.png"}], "audio": "s10_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "This generates the output file.", "audio": "s11_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-e88dfef4-1f83-44c1-8347-e3b50c0d59f5.png"}], "audio": "s11_0.mp3"}, {"slide": [{"text": "And all the audio files, so your Words and Pictures book is ready to play.", "audio": "s12_1.mp3", "img": "https://coggle-images.s3.amazonaws.com/553c9677f199f5492994bf52-b3ec40b1-c5ac-4def-b8ce-dcf6885a37fe.png"}], "audio": "s12_0.mp3"}]}